gee_result_step = geeglm(as.formula(paste0("STEP_COUNT ~ week_category_new_c + study_week + ", Control_var)), 
                         data = data %>% drop_na(STEP_COUNT,all_of(Cov_set))  ,weights = w*r_w, id = UserID, scale.fix = T)
summary(gee_result_step)

                    SE = sqrt(vcov_gee ),
                    Method = "WCLS")
